      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HE'S A PEARL (8) goes very well over this trip including two wins. Recorded a 4 length win (25.53) in a NG last time at this track. Looks a leading chance on best. FINE SHINE (1) continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at his last four runs. Last start finished 2nd on March 8 over 457m at this track behind HE'S A PEARL beaten 4 lengths (25.81) in a NG. Boasts two wins from two starts out of this box. Overdue and gets his chance. SECRET BANDIT (2) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by 2.5 lengths at this track in a handy 25.60 beating CUMBRIA BENNY. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. Leading chance again. CLASSY BANDIT (3) is a last-start placegetter in fast time – sure to have admirers.",
